title: Message in a Bottle (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor wants to get a message to her admirer in any way possible, whether it's through this bop of a song or through a bottle.. she wants them to know what's on her mind!
What do you think of this song? What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Let us know!
